        ")\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/shiny_app/minty_vb.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "[`{shinyWidgets}` ]{.s-title} \n",
        "\n",
        "`shinyWidgets::shinyWidgetsGallery()` for full gallery\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/shinywidgets.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
