        "\n",
        "# HTML and CSS\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/htmltools.png){width=20% fig-align=\"center\"} \n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        ":::: {.columns}\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"60%\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "Create custom HTML elements and CSS styles directly in R Shiny with `{htmltools}`\n",
        "\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.column width=\"40%\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "- `tags$p()`\n",
        "- `tags$div()`\n",
        "- `tags$img()`\n",
        "- `tags$style()`\n",
        "\n",
        ":::\n",
        "::::\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"ui.R\"}\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "\n",
        "htmltools::tags$img(\n",
        "  src = \"sablefish.jpg\", # adding sablefish image to sidebar\n",
        "  width = \"100%\",\n",
        "  style = \"margin-top: 1rem; border-radius: 6px;\" #CSS\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "htmltools::tags$p(\n",
        "  \"Sablefish are deep-sea fish found in the North Pacific, known for their rich flavor and high oil content.\",\n",
        "  style = \"color: teal; font-size: 0.8rem; font-style: italic;\"\n",
        ")\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/shiny_app/minty_sable.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "[CSS]{.title} \n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "[Heirarchy of CSS]{.s-title}\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Inline (Highest priority)\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"ui.R\"}\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "\n",
        "htmltools::tags$img(\n",
        "  src = \"sablefish.jpg\",\n",
        "  style = \"margin-top: 1rem; border-radius: 6px;\" #CSS\n",
        ")\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "2. Internal (medium priority)\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"ui.R\"}\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "\n",
        "tags$head(tags$style()) # calling CSS rules directly in the app\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "3. `External CSS (Lowest priority, but best practice)`\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"ui.R\"}\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "\n",
        "tags$head(tags$link()) # calling an external CSS file out of app\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Linking external CSS file\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"ui.R\"}\n",
        "#| code-line-numbers: \"7-12\"\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "ui <- page_navbar(\n",
        "  title = \"Palmer Penguins Explorer\",\n",
        "  theme = bs_theme(\n",
        "    #... Theme code...\n",
        "  ),\n",
        "\n",
        "  # Linking extrnal CSS file\n",
        "  tags$head(tags$link(\n",
        "    rel = \"stylesheet\",\n",
        "    type = \"text/css\", # type of file\n",
        "    href = \"styles.css\" # file name\n",
        "  )),\n",
        "  # ...Other UI code...\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/img_css.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/shiny_app/inspector.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "Targeting the **class** of an element\n",
        "\n",
        "```{.r filename=\"styles.css\"}\n",
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "#| echo: true\n",
        "\n",
        ".control-label { /* changing label styles */\n",
        "    font-weight: bold !important;\n",
        "    font-size: 1.1rem !important;\n",
        "    color: #021d31ff !important;\n",
        "    text-decoration: underline !important;\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        ".card-header { /* changing card header styles */\n",
        "    background-color: teal !important;\n",
        "    color: white !important;\n",
        "    font-style: italic !important;\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        ".bslib-sidebar-layout>.main { /* changing main panel background */\n",
        "    background-color: #021d31ff !important;\n",
        "}\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "![](images/shiny_app/bslib_css.png){.round fig-align=\"center\" width=100%}\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Common Selector Types\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Element Selector**: targets all elements of a specific type (e.g., `p`, `h1`, `div`).\n",
        "2. **Class Selector**: targets elements with a specific class attribute (e.g., `.my-class`).\n",
        "3. **ID Selector**: targets a single element with a specific id attribute (e.g., `#my-id`).\n",
        "4. **Attribute Selector**: targets element attribute (e.g., `input[type=\"text\"]`).\n",
        "5. **Pseudo-class Selector**: targets element state (e.g., `a:hover` for links when hovered).\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
